<p>The timeline display gives you detailed information about broadcasting playlist. You can drag the timeline and click on the items to get more information.</p>

<p>Timeline will focus on current moment after 60 seconds so that this page can also be left open. It will also reload the data at that time.</p>

<%= start_form_tag :action => 'timeline' %>
  <select name="channel_id" onChange="javascript: this.form.submit()">
    <%= options_from_collection_for_select(Channel.find(:all), "id", "name", @channel_id) %>
  </select>
<%= submit_tag "Update" %>
<%= end_form_tag %>


<div id="playlist_timeline" style="height: 600px; border: 1px solid #aaa"></div>
<input type="submit" value="Toggle centering (off)" onClick='javascript:if(toggleCenter()) this.value="Toggle centering (on)"; else this.value="Toggle centering (off)";'>test</input>

<div class="controls" id="controls">
</div>
